{"tid":2218402,"cid":18,"subCid":6,"title":"自己諗左啲揭尾故","createTime":"2020-09-26T07:30:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-06T13:05:17.000Z","uid":80163,"like":27,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"8c592338bba84f345778b1dfba012f2aeea0ee7e","tid":2218402,"uid":80163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T07:30:21.000Z","msg":"平時係網上搵個啲已經太多人玩過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以我自己試左諗下揭尾故<br />\n想大家比啲意見我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第一個故事叫鏡子<br />\n<br />\n係某國有一位女仕 佢好有錢 咩都買得起 <br />\n但佢唯一最唔鍾意既係 照鏡<br />\n傳聞佢發跡前係一間大宅做過女僕<br />\n點解佢會咁抗拒照鏡呢?<br />\n<br />\n第二個故事叫 密室殺人事件 01<br />\n<br />\n一名探員收到報告 有個男人死左係一間破舊既倉庫入面<br />\n倉庫無任何窗 門被鎖住 屋頂有幾個細細既洞<br />\n男人被綁起椅子上 頭比人固定向上<br />\n地上面有幾張有水跡既紙<br />\n紙上面係有化開左個字跡<br />\n大約可以見到有張寫住「人」同「渣」<br />\n男人係點死既呢?<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/5PIDs0O8I10\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F5PIDs0O8I10&d=I0uz%2BNPXkLchxl3mN3HTu4hgI2KbCNwkzH4ce58ZUDE%3D&h=b6e074ac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/5PIDs0O8I10</a>"},{"pid":"c19b8be7ebfe3b9dccfa2f3baa0a6f2f522bfcfb","tid":2218402,"uid":180124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T07:41:15.000Z","msg":"留名等開估"},{"pid":"60cb65bf696172bcdf3a99aa9706268759379935","tid":2218402,"uid":234589,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T07:53:41.000Z","msg":"自己畫晒成個故事出嚟好有心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c60f6cba6f6b9a4fc5a06f4e82cdce6c9c06320e","tid":2218402,"uid":234589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T08:16:48.000Z","msg":"Ivan成日負責整理故事"},{"pid":"953c7122a73f8ad27e665088ddb687506bc6488f","tid":2218402,"uid":118922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T09:42:55.000Z","msg":"第一個 又係果D殺左女主人 照女主人個樣整容<br />\n第二個 浸死??"},{"pid":"42e547516d939a0ad3c6fe825d35cc1000b527ec","tid":2